From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 13:03:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Responsive fixes + photos slider

- Convert photos & video grid into a horizontal scroll-snap slider with
  prev/next buttons (works on mobile and desktop)
- Hero: override inline margin-left:500px on tablet/mobile so content
  stops bleeding off-screen; stack CTA buttons full-width on small phones
- Team card: override inline 831x400 px dimensions on tablet/mobile so
  the card fits the viewport
- Add a hamburger toggle for the top nav at <880px (menu collapses into
  a stacked panel)
- Coaching modal: tighter padding and single-column field rows on small
  screens
- Section padding and titles tuned for narrow widths

https://claude.ai/code/session_01CQhaur5bgTcTG5y3ok9zon
